==English==
===Noun===
'''[[Australian]] [[rhyming slang]]'''

#A [[cant]] used by [[Australian]]'s in which a word or phrase is replaced by a [[rhyme|rhyming]] word or phrase, this word or phrase then often being abbreviated to its first [[syllable]] or syllables, or its first word.

